always leave beginners out here like this?

::Koj::

Koj looks at the massive broken wing. "There is no way the 2 of us can move 
it or I can repair the ship without hands you know."

::Inu-Yasha::

Inu-Yasha looks at Koj and Growls.

::Koj::

Koj steps back "Ok ok i'll try." As he bites down on the wing with his 
teeth.

::Inu-Yasha::

Flies up and land on the wing digging his claws into it.

::Both::
Start pulling doing little good if any.
